{
  "spec": {
    "title": "WebMCP",
    "url": "https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "name": "notify documents of a tool change",
      "href": "https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#notify-documents-of-a-tool-change",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"notify-documents-of-a-tool-change\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">notify documents of a tool change</dfn> given a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#document\" id=\"ref-for-document\">Document</a></code> <var>tool owner</var> and a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list\" id=\"ref-for-list①\">list</a> of\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/browsers.html#concept-origin\" id=\"ref-for-concept-origin①\">origins</a> <var>exposed origins</var>, run these steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#assert\" id=\"ref-for-assert\">Assert</a>: these steps are running on <var>tool owner</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#relevant-agent\" id=\"ref-for-relevant-agent\">relevant agent</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-agent-event-loop\" id=\"ref-for-concept-agent-event-loop\">event loop</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>navigablesToNotify</var> be <var>tool owner</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#node-navigable\" id=\"ref-for-node-navigable\">node navigable</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#nav-traversable\" id=\"ref-for-nav-traversable\">traversable navigable</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#descendant-navigables\" id=\"ref-for-descendant-navigables\">descendant navigables</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-iterate\" id=\"ref-for-list-iterate\">For each</a> <var>navigable</var> of <var>navigablesToNotify</var>:",
          "rationale": "let",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>targetDocument</var> be <var>navigable</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#nav-document\" id=\"ref-for-nav-document\">active document</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>targetDocument</var> is not <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/iframe-embed-object.html#allowed-to-use\" id=\"ref-for-allowed-to-use\">allowed to use</a> the \"<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#permissiondef-tools\" id=\"ref-for-permissiondef-tools\">tools</a></code>\" feature, then\n  <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#iteration-continue\" id=\"ref-for-iteration-continue\">continue</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>If <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#tool-is-visible-to-an-origin\" id=\"ref-for-tool-is-visible-to-an-origin\">tool is visible to an origin</a> given <var>tool owner</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document-origin\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document-origin\">origin</a>, <var>exposed\n  origins</var>, and <var>targetDocument</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-document-origin\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document-origin①\">origin</a>, then <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#queue-a-global-task\" id=\"ref-for-queue-a-global-task\">queue a global task</a> on the\n  <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#webmcp-task-source\" id=\"ref-for-webmcp-task-source\">webmcp task source</a> given <var>targetDocument</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global\">relevant global object</a> to <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-event-fire\" id=\"ref-for-concept-event-fire\">fire an event</a> named <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#eventdef-modelcontext-toolchange\" id=\"ref-for-eventdef-modelcontext-toolchange\">toolchange</a></code> at <var>targetDocument</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global①\">relevant global object</a>’s\n  <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/C#associated-navigator\" id=\"ref-for-associated-navigator\">associated <code>Navigator</code></a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#navigator-associated-modelcontext\" id=\"ref-for-navigator-associated-modelcontext\">associated <code>ModelContext</code></a>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "tool is visible to an origin",
      "href": "https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#tool-is-visible-to-an-origin",
      "html": "To determine if a <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"tool-is-visible-to-an-origin\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">tool is visible to an origin</dfn> given an <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/browsers.html#concept-origin\" id=\"ref-for-concept-origin②\">origin</a> <var>tool owner origin</var>,\na <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list\" id=\"ref-for-list②\">list</a> of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/browsers.html#concept-origin\" id=\"ref-for-concept-origin③\">origins</a> <var>exposed origins</var>, and an <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/browsers.html#concept-origin\" id=\"ref-for-concept-origin④\">origin</a> <var>target origin</var>, run these steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>tool owner origin</var> is <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/browsers.html#same-origin\" id=\"ref-for-same-origin\">same origin</a> with <var>target origin</var>, then return true.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-iterate\" id=\"ref-for-list-iterate①\">For each</a> <var>origin</var> of <var>exposed origins</var>:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>target origin</var> is <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/browsers.html#same-origin\" id=\"ref-for-same-origin①\">same origin</a> with <var>origin</var>, then return true.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return false.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "model context/unregister a tool",
      "href": "https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#model-context-unregister-a-tool",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-for=\"model context\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"model-context-unregister-a-tool\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">unregister a tool</dfn> given a <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#modelcontext\" id=\"ref-for-modelcontext\">ModelContext</a></code> <var>modelContext</var> and a\n<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#string\" id=\"ref-for-string⑤\">string</a> <var>tool name</var>, run these steps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#assert\" id=\"ref-for-assert①\">Assert</a>: these steps are running on <var>modelContext</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#relevant-agent\" id=\"ref-for-relevant-agent①\">relevant agent</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-agent-event-loop\" id=\"ref-for-concept-agent-event-loop①\">event loop</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>tool map</var> be <var>modelContext</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#modelcontext-internal-context\" id=\"ref-for-modelcontext-internal-context\">internal context</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#model-context-tool-map\" id=\"ref-for-model-context-tool-map①\">tool map</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#assert\" id=\"ref-for-assert②\">Assert</a> <var>tool map</var>[<var>tool name</var>] <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists\">exists</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>exposed origins</var> be <var>tool map</var>[<var>tool name</var>]'s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#tool-definition-exposed-origins\" id=\"ref-for-tool-definition-exposed-origins\">exposed origins</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-remove\" id=\"ref-for-map-remove\">Remove</a> <var>tool map</var>[<var>tool name</var>].</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Run <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#notify-documents-of-a-tool-change\" id=\"ref-for-notify-documents-of-a-tool-change\">notify documents of a tool change</a> given <var>modelContext</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global②\">relevant global object</a>’s\n <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#concept-document-window\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document-window\">associated <code>Document</code></a> and <var>exposed origins</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Navigator/modelContext",
      "href": "https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-navigator-modelcontext",
      "html": "The <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled idl-code has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-for=\"Navigator\" data-dfn-type=\"attribute\" data-export=\"\" id=\"dom-navigator-modelcontext\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\"><code>modelContext</code></dfn> getter steps are:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>If <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#navigator-associated-modelcontext\" id=\"ref-for-navigator-associated-modelcontext③\">associated <code>ModelContext</code></a>’s\n <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#modelcontext-creation-document\" id=\"ref-for-modelcontext-creation-document\"> creation <code>Document</code></a> does not equal <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this①\">this</a>’s\n <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global⑤\">relevant global object</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#concept-document-window\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document-window③\">associated <code>Document</code></a>, then set\n <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this②\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#navigator-associated-modelcontext\" id=\"ref-for-navigator-associated-modelcontext④\">associated <code>ModelContext</code></a> to a\n <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#new\" id=\"ref-for-new①\">new</a> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#modelcontext\" id=\"ref-for-modelcontext⑦\">ModelContext</a></code> object.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Return <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this③\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#navigator-associated-modelcontext\" id=\"ref-for-navigator-associated-modelcontext⑤\">associated <code>ModelContext</code></a>\n object.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "ModelContext/registerTool(tool, options)",
      "href": "https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-modelcontext-registertool",
      "html": "The <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled idl-code has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-for=\"ModelContext\" data-dfn-type=\"method\" data-export=\"\" data-lt=\"registerTool(tool, options)|registerTool(tool)\" id=\"dom-modelcontext-registertool\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\"><code>registerTool(<var>tool</var>, <var>options</var>)</code></dfn> method steps are:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>tool owner</var> be <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this④\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global⑥\">relevant global object</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/nav-history-apis.html#concept-document-window\" id=\"ref-for-concept-document-window④\">associated\n <code>Document</code></a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>tool owner</var> is not <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#fully-active\" id=\"ref-for-fully-active\">fully active</a>, then <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-throw\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-throw\">throw</a> an\n \"<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror\" id=\"ref-for-invalidstateerror\">InvalidStateError</a></code>\" <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMException\">DOMException</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>tool owner</var> is not <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/iframe-embed-object.html#allowed-to-use\" id=\"ref-for-allowed-to-use①\">allowed to use</a> the \"<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#permissiondef-tools\" id=\"ref-for-permissiondef-tools①\">tools</a></code>\" feature, then <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-throw\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-throw①\">throw</a> a\n \"<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#notallowederror\" id=\"ref-for-notallowederror\">NotAllowedError</a></code>\" <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMException①\">DOMException</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>tool map</var> be <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this⑤\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#modelcontext-internal-context\" id=\"ref-for-modelcontext-internal-context①\">internal context</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#model-context-tool-map\" id=\"ref-for-model-context-tool-map②\">tool map</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>tool name</var> be <var>tool</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-modelcontexttool-name\" id=\"ref-for-dom-modelcontexttool-name①\">name</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>tool title</var> be <var>tool</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-modelcontexttool-title\" id=\"ref-for-dom-modelcontexttool-title①\">title</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>tool map</var>[<var>tool name</var>] <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists①\">exists</a>, then <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-throw\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-throw②\">throw</a> an <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror\" id=\"ref-for-invalidstateerror①\">InvalidStateError</a></code>\n <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMException②\">DOMException</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>tool name</var> or <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-modelcontexttool-description\" id=\"ref-for-dom-modelcontexttool-description①\">description</a></code> is an empty string, then\n <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-throw\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-throw③\">throw</a> an <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror\" id=\"ref-for-invalidstateerror②\">InvalidStateError</a></code> <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMException③\">DOMException</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If either <var>tool name</var> is the empty string, or its <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#string-length\" id=\"ref-for-string-length①\">length</a> is greater than 128, or if\n <var>tool name</var> contains a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#code-point\" id=\"ref-for-code-point①\">code point</a> that is not an <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#ascii-alphanumeric\" id=\"ref-for-ascii-alphanumeric①\">ASCII alphanumeric</a>, U+005F (_),\n U+002D (-), or U+002E (.), then <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-throw\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-throw④\">throw</a> an <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#invalidstateerror\" id=\"ref-for-invalidstateerror③\">InvalidStateError</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>stringified input schema</var> be the empty string.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>If <var>tool</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-modelcontexttool-inputschema\" id=\"ref-for-dom-modelcontexttool-inputschema②\">inputSchema</a></code> <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists②\">exists</a>, then set <var>stringified input schema</var>\n to the result of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#serialize-a-javascript-value-to-a-json-string\" id=\"ref-for-serialize-a-javascript-value-to-a-json-string\">serializing a JavaScript value to a JSON string</a>, given <var>tool</var>’s\n <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-modelcontexttool-inputschema\" id=\"ref-for-dom-modelcontexttool-inputschema③\">inputSchema</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>read-only hint</var> be true if <var>tool</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-modelcontexttool-annotations\" id=\"ref-for-dom-modelcontexttool-annotations\">annotations</a></code> <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists③\">exists</a> and\n its <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-toolannotations-readonlyhint\" id=\"ref-for-dom-toolannotations-readonlyhint\">readOnlyHint</a></code> is true. Otherwise, let it be false.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>untrusted content hint</var> be true if <var>tool</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-modelcontexttool-annotations\" id=\"ref-for-dom-modelcontexttool-annotations①\">annotations</a></code> <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists④\">exists</a> and\n its <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-toolannotations-untrustedcontenthint\" id=\"ref-for-dom-toolannotations-untrustedcontenthint\">untrustedContentHint</a></code> is true. Otherwise, let it be false.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>signal</var> be <var>options</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-modelcontextregistertooloptions-signal\" id=\"ref-for-dom-modelcontextregistertooloptions-signal\">signal</a></code>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var>signal</var> <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists⑤\">exists</a>, then:",
          "rationale": "if",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>If <var>signal</var> is <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#abortsignal-aborted\" id=\"ref-for-abortsignal-aborted\">aborted</a>, then optionally <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://console.spec.whatwg.org/#report-a-warning-to-the-console\" id=\"ref-for-report-a-warning-to-the-console\">report a warning to the console</a>\n  indicating that the tool was not registered because the <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#abortsignal\" id=\"ref-for-abortsignal\">AbortSignal</a></code> was already\n  <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#abortsignal-aborted\" id=\"ref-for-abortsignal-aborted①\">aborted</a>, and return.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#abortsignal-add\" id=\"ref-for-abortsignal-add\">Add an abort algorithm</a> to <var>signal</var> that <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#model-context-unregister-a-tool\" id=\"ref-for-model-context-unregister-a-tool\">unregisters a tool</a> given <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this⑥\">this</a> and <var>tool name</var>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>exposed origins</var> be an empty <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list\" id=\"ref-for-list③\">list</a> of <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/browsers.html#concept-origin\" id=\"ref-for-concept-origin⑤\">origins</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "If <var>options</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-modelcontextregistertooloptions-exposedto\" id=\"ref-for-dom-modelcontextregistertooloptions-exposedto\">exposedTo</a></code> <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-exists\" id=\"ref-for-map-exists⑥\">exists</a>, then:",
          "rationale": "for",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-iterate\" id=\"ref-for-list-iterate②\">For each</a> <var>origin</var> of <var>options</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-modelcontextregistertooloptions-exposedto\" id=\"ref-for-dom-modelcontextregistertooloptions-exposedto①\">exposedTo</a></code>:",
              "rationale": "let",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "html": "<p>Let <var>parsedURL</var> be the result of running the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-url-parser\" id=\"ref-for-concept-url-parser\">URL parser</a> on <var>origin</var>.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "html": "<p>If <var>parsedURL</var> is failure or its <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-url-origin\" id=\"ref-for-concept-url-origin\">origin</a> is not <a data-link-type=\"abstract-op\" href=\"https://w3c.github.io/webappsec-secure-contexts/#is-origin-trustworthy\" id=\"ref-for-is-origin-trustworthy\">potentially trustworthy</a>, then <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#dfn-throw\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-throw⑤\">throw</a> an \"<code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#securityerror\" id=\"ref-for-securityerror\">SecurityError</a></code>\"\n <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#idl-DOMException\" id=\"ref-for-idl-DOMException④\">DOMException</a></code>.</p>"
                },
                {
                  "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-append\" id=\"ref-for-list-append\">Append</a> <var>parsedURL</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#concept-url-origin\" id=\"ref-for-concept-url-origin①\">origin</a> to <var>exposed origins</var>.</p>"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>tool definition</var> be a new <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#tool-definition\" id=\"ref-for-tool-definition①\">tool definition</a>, with the following <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#struct-item\" id=\"ref-for-struct-item②\">items</a>:</p>\n      <dl>\n       <dt data-md=\"\"><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#tool-definition-name\" id=\"ref-for-tool-definition-name①\">name</a>\n       </dt><dd data-md=\"\">\n        <p><var>tool name</var></p>\n       </dd><dt data-md=\"\"><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#tool-definition-title\" id=\"ref-for-tool-definition-title\">title</a>\n       </dt><dd data-md=\"\">\n        <p><var>tool title</var></p>\n       </dd><dt data-md=\"\"><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#tool-definition-description\" id=\"ref-for-tool-definition-description\">description</a>\n       </dt><dd data-md=\"\">\n        <p><var>tool</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-modelcontexttool-description\" id=\"ref-for-dom-modelcontexttool-description②\">description</a></code></p>\n       </dd><dt data-md=\"\"><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#tool-definition-input-schema\" id=\"ref-for-tool-definition-input-schema\">input schema</a>\n       </dt><dd data-md=\"\">\n        <p><var>stringified input schema</var></p>\n       </dd><dt data-md=\"\"><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#tool-definition-execute-steps\" id=\"ref-for-tool-definition-execute-steps\">execute steps</a>\n       </dt><dd data-md=\"\">\n        <p>steps that invoke <var>tool</var>’s <code class=\"idl\"><a data-link-type=\"idl\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-modelcontexttool-execute\" id=\"ref-for-dom-modelcontexttool-execute\">execute</a></code></p>\n       </dd><dt data-md=\"\"><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#tool-definition-read-only-hint\" id=\"ref-for-tool-definition-read-only-hint\">read-only hint</a>\n       </dt><dd data-md=\"\">\n        <p><var>read-only hint</var></p>\n       </dd><dt data-md=\"\"><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#tool-definition-untrusted-content-hint\" id=\"ref-for-tool-definition-untrusted-content-hint\">untrusted content hint</a>\n       </dt><dd data-md=\"\">\n        <p><var>untrusted content hint</var></p>\n       </dd><dt data-md=\"\"><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#tool-definition-exposed-origins\" id=\"ref-for-tool-definition-exposed-origins①\">exposed origins</a>\n       </dt><dd data-md=\"\">\n        <p><var>exposed origins</var></p>\n      </dd></dl>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Set <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webidl.spec.whatwg.org/#this\" id=\"ref-for-this⑦\">this</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#modelcontext-internal-context\" id=\"ref-for-modelcontext-internal-context②\">internal context</a>[<var>tool name</var>] to <var>tool definition</var>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Run <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#notify-documents-of-a-tool-change\" id=\"ref-for-notify-documents-of-a-tool-change①\">notify documents of a tool change</a> given <var>tool owner</var> and <var>exposed origins</var>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "ModelContextClient/requestUserInteraction(callback)",
      "href": "https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#dom-modelcontextclient-requestuserinteraction",
      "html": "The <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled idl-code has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-for=\"ModelContextClient\" data-dfn-type=\"method\" data-export=\"\" id=\"dom-modelcontextclient-requestuserinteraction\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\"><code>requestUserInteraction(<var>callback</var>)</code></dfn> method steps are:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>TODO: fill this out.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "synthesize a declarative JSON Schema object algorithm",
      "href": "https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#synthesize-a-declarative-json-schema-object-algorithm",
      "html": "The <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"synthesize-a-declarative-json-schema-object-algorithm\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">synthesize a declarative JSON Schema object algorithm</dfn>, given a <code><a data-link-type=\"element\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/forms.html#the-form-element\" id=\"ref-for-the-form-element①\">form</a></code> element\n<var>form</var>, runs the following steps. They return a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#ordered-map\" id=\"ref-for-ordered-map①\">map</a> representing a JSON Schema object.\n<a data-link-type=\"biblio\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#biblio-json-schema\" title=\"JSON Schema: A Media Type for Describing JSON Documents\">[JSON-SCHEMA]</a>",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p>TODO: Derive a conformant JSON Schema object from <var>form</var> and its <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/forms.html#form-associated-element\" id=\"ref-for-form-associated-element①\">form-associated elements</a>.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "perform an observation",
      "href": "https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#perform-an-observation",
      "html": "To <dfn class=\"dfn-paneled has-dfn-panel\" data-dfn-type=\"dfn\" data-noexport=\"\" id=\"perform-an-observation\" role=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\">perform an observation</dfn> given a <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#top-level-traversable\" id=\"ref-for-top-level-traversable\">top-level traversable</a> <var>traversable</var>, run these\nsteps:",
      "rationale": ".algorithm",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#assert\" id=\"ref-for-assert③\">Assert</a>: This algorithm is running in the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#browsers-agent\" id=\"ref-for-browsers-agent⑦\">browser agent</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#ai-agent-queue\" id=\"ref-for-ai-agent-queue\">AI agent queue</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p><a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#assert\" id=\"ref-for-assert④\">Assert</a>: <var>traversable</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#nav-document\" id=\"ref-for-nav-document①\">active document</a> is not <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#fully-active\" id=\"ref-for-fully-active①\">fully active</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>observation</var> be a new <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#observation\" id=\"ref-for-observation②\">observation</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Let <var>flat descendants</var> be the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#inclusive-descendant-navigables\" id=\"ref-for-inclusive-descendant-navigables\">inclusive descendant navigables</a> of <var>traversable</var>’s\n <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#nav-document\" id=\"ref-for-nav-document②\">active document</a>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#list-iterate\" id=\"ref-for-list-iterate③\">For each</a> <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#navigable\" id=\"ref-for-navigable\">navigable</a> <var>descendant</var> of <var>flat descendants</var>:",
          "rationale": "let",
          "steps": [
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>document</var> be <var>descendant</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/document-sequences.html#nav-document\" id=\"ref-for-nav-document③\">active document</a>’s.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Let <var>id</var> be <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#document-unique-id\" id=\"ref-for-document-unique-id①\">unique ID</a>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "html": "<p>Set <var>observation</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#observation-tool-map\" id=\"ref-for-observation-tool-map\">tool map</a>[<var>id</var>] = <var>document</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#concept-relevant-global\" id=\"ref-for-concept-relevant-global⑨\">relevant global object</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/C#associated-navigator\" id=\"ref-for-associated-navigator①\">associated <code>Navigator</code></a>’s\n  <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#navigator-associated-modelcontext\" id=\"ref-for-navigator-associated-modelcontext⑥\">associated <code>ModelContext</code></a>’s\n  <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#modelcontext-internal-context\" id=\"ref-for-modelcontext-internal-context③\">internal context</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#model-context-tool-map\" id=\"ref-for-model-context-tool-map③\">tool map</a>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#map-getting-the-values\" id=\"ref-for-map-getting-the-values②\">values</a>, which are\n  <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#tool-definition\" id=\"ref-for-tool-definition③\">tool definitions</a>.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Perform any <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#implementation-defined\" id=\"ref-for-implementation-defined①\">implementation-defined</a> steps to add anything to <var>observation</var> that the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#user-agent\" id=\"ref-for-user-agent③\">user agent</a> might deem useful or necessary, besides just populating the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#observation-tool-map\" id=\"ref-for-observation-tool-map①\">tool map</a>.\n This might include annotated screenshots of the page, parts of the accessibility tree, etc.</p>"
        },
        {
          "html": "<p>Perform any <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://infra.spec.whatwg.org/#implementation-defined\" id=\"ref-for-implementation-defined②\">implementation-defined</a> steps with <var>observation</var> and the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#browsers-agent\" id=\"ref-for-browsers-agent⑧\">browser agent</a>, to\n expose the <var>observation</var>’s <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#observation-tool-map\" id=\"ref-for-observation-tool-map②\">tool map</a> to the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#browsers-agent\" id=\"ref-for-browsers-agent⑨\">browser agent</a> in whatever way it\n accepts.</p>\n      \n      <p><strong class=\"advisement\"> Implementations are expected to convey to the <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#browsers-agent\" id=\"ref-for-browsers-agent①①\">browser agent</a> any relevant\n   security information associated with <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://webmachinelearning.github.io/webmcp/#tool-definition\" id=\"ref-for-tool-definition④\">tool definitions</a>, such as the originating <a data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/browsers.html#concept-origin\" id=\"ref-for-concept-origin⑥\">origin</a>,\n   among other things, so that the backing model has an idea of the different parties at play, and\n   can most safely carry out the end user’s intent.</strong></p>"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}